des: KUPI is “#1 for Country Radio” in East Idaho, with the largest coverage area of any country station in Eastern Idaho. We support our listeners every day with a talented cast of On-air talent to drive interest in our local community. Everything we do is intended to help the advertiser meet budgets and projections. There are no surprises; listeners get the best music these country artists have to offer.
